| Coding standards | `knowledge-base/08-coding-standards.md` |
| Module specs | `knowledge-base/modules/M01..M16` |
| Sprint plan | `knowledge-base/sprints/sprint-00..18` |
| Prompts | `knowledge-base/prompts/` |

## Tech stack (bắt buộc)

- **Backend**: .NET 8, EF Core, PostgreSQL 16, Redis, Hangfire, SignalR
- **Web**: Next.js 14 (App Router), TypeScript, Ant Design Pro, TanStack Query, Zustand
- **Mobile**: Flutter 3.x, Riverpod 2, Dio, Hive

## Quy tắc khi generate code

1. Dùng thuật ngữ domain từ `01-glossary.md` (PG, Leader, BUH, Store, Shift, Face Verification...)
2. Business logic theo `06-business-rules.md` — trích dẫn BR-xxx
3. Endpoints theo `05-api-conventions.md`; entities theo `04-data-model.md`
4. Tham chiếu AC-xxx khi implement acceptance criteria
5. Giải thích bằng tiếng Việt; code/identifiers bằng tiếng Anh; user-visible strings song ngữ vi+en
6. Không implement scope ngoài Phase 1 (xem `knowledge-base/prompts/system-prompt.md`)

Chi tiết đầy đủ: `@knowledge-base/prompts/system-prompt.md`
